SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-326 - Pembina NGL Corporation and Pembina Resource Services Canada
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-326 to Pembina NGL Corporation and Pembina Resource Services Canada to export propane from a marine export terminal on the west coast of Canada and points along the Canada-United States border where railway crossings occur, British Columbia.
